title: Mars Argo vs. Poppy vs. Charlotte.
description:
Titanic Sinclair always wanted to be on TMZ, and now he is, for all the wrong reasons: http://www.tmz.com/2018/04/17/youtube-legal-feud-titanic-sinclair-mars-argo-thatpoppy/
Other coverage includes Repzilla: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXgGxoK-fsv1ScBHE7lYi_Q/search?query=poppy
Further updates from Mars Argo superfan Mandy Monett:
https://twitter.com/mandymonett
She (M.M.) also has a youtube channel with acoustic cover versions of Mars Argo songs: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh0Zt1vUeBzgHVgb9k9AXsg/videos
